{"tid":736520,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"尖子配「新神科」  港大多個學院收錄全港最高分精英","createTime":"2018-07-10T09:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T05:56:38.000Z","uid":14170,"like":13,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"6abde82c92e953587c621dd8fad6c76620371cfd","tid":736520,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:50:37.000Z","msg":"除醫科和法律課程外，入讀不同學術範疇的全港最高分精英，皆以港大為首選。而被學生視為「新神科」的生物醫學學士，取錄人數比去年增加4成之餘，整體收生分數出色。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/10/174949_c696fb3c0d1e9fbe69b8f6bc1ac4717f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2F174949_c696fb3c0d1e9fbe69b8f6bc1ac4717f.png&h=027a67ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了多個學科均取錄了全港頂尖的聯招生外，獲港大取錄的應屆文憑試考生的整體成績優秀，各科平均分數均為全港之冠，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/10/175015_91caa19c0dfbc214ee17f0eed0006076.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2F175015_91caa19c0dfbc214ee17f0eed0006076.png&h=16cd1d74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n# 香港中學文憑考試成績換算: 5**=7, 5*=6, 5=5, 4=4, 3=3, 2=2, 1=1"},{"pid":"864fad3a7dc2cf95fb15bdabd787d3412be21cd7","tid":736520,"uid":36739,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:53:54.000Z","msg":"精英大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e69ed748f93bce95eeeae43acf25f714c7fa14e","tid":736520,"uid":29929,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:54:28.000Z","msg":"地球香港大學領先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e4c1c4f7dbf11399dc8f447973918a10215623","tid":736520,"uid":14170,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:55:23.000Z","msg":"1. MBBS BDS LLB, 5** x7<br />\n2. IBGM 5** x6<br />\n3. BBiomedSc <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">BEng</span> BA, 5** x5<span style=\"color: orange;\"></span